title: An R Package for Analyzing Data from Stepped Wedge Cluster Randomized Trials
text: steppedwedge open-source R package designed analyzing data stepped wedge cluster randomized trials. Functions given checking/visualizing datasets estimating various treatment effect parameters, including immediate treatment effect (ITE), exposure time averaged treatment effect (ETATE), calendar time averaged treatment effect (CTATE).
